snippet: Joao Barbosa and Christian Fittipaldi won the TUDOR United SportsCar Championship race at Road America on Sunday for their third victory of the year in Action Express Racing's No. 5 Corvette....

headline.print_headline: Barbosa, Fittipaldi Win at Road America
headline.main: Barbosa, Fittipaldi Win at Road America

lead_paragraph: Joao Barbosa and Christian Fittipaldi won the TUDOR United SportsCar Championship race at Road America on Sunday for their third victory of the year in Action Express Racing's No. 5 Corvette.
